  "detailed_description": "There are tens of thousands of different wonderful platform jumping levels, created by the most talented players all over the world. If you love platform jumping, you can't miss it.<br><br>2D platformer runner game with all levels completed by players, no official maps, and ultra-high freedom.<br><br>Highly customizable, all items are supported to be redrawn in the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/07ca577d17cee828f5740d398fb9fb7c.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/07ca577d17cee828f5740d398fb9fb7c.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/07ca577d17cee828f5740d398fb9fb7c.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Custom item function, control monster logic without programming<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/ac7e63af20f0fbce5d053c1477236c72.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/ac7e63af20f0fbce5d053c1477236c72.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/ac7e63af20f0fbce5d053c1477236c72.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Extremely difficult jumping and dodging.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/d5ecb717d9e5734a3691bfcfc68301dd.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/d5ecb717d9e5734a3691bfcfc68301dd.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/d5ecb717d9e5734a3691bfcfc68301dd.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defeat the boss and pass the levels together in the underground city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/901a2a40f4c20d867591320f3ddfd830.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/901a2a40f4c20d867591320f3ddfd830.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/901a2a40f4c20d867591320f3ddfd830.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/a1aaff24b98abd0484392a488c8663fa.avif?t=1721397921\" width=558 height=298 /></span><br><br>The game contains a variety of items, such as spring, gravity control, weapon, iron head, iron shoes, shell, handgun, consecutive jumping, teleportation portal, and so on.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/a99d9aa07647947696372baf423dfdb5.avif?t=1721397921\" width=558 height=298 /></span><br><br>Feature-rich creative panel ignites your imagination.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/00fdf7196bdbe09aa1bcb35c2545118c.avif?t=1721397921\" width=558 height=514 /></span><br><br>Players can directly create pixel art in the game and use it directly in the editor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/c5bfd41debc3c0afdbed3e853d40475e.avif?t=1721397921\" width=800 height=186 /></span><br><br>Complete social functions allow players to compete with each other in terms of map-making and runner skills.",
  "about_the_game": "There are tens of thousands of different wonderful platform jumping levels, created by the most talented players all over the world. If you love platform jumping, you can't miss it.<br><br>2D platformer runner game with all levels completed by players, no official maps, and ultra-high freedom.<br><br>Highly customizable, all items are supported to be redrawn in the game.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/07ca577d17cee828f5740d398fb9fb7c.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/07ca577d17cee828f5740d398fb9fb7c.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/07ca577d17cee828f5740d398fb9fb7c.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Custom item function, control monster logic without programming<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/ac7e63af20f0fbce5d053c1477236c72.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/ac7e63af20f0fbce5d053c1477236c72.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/ac7e63af20f0fbce5d053c1477236c72.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Extremely difficult jumping and dodging.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/d5ecb717d9e5734a3691bfcfc68301dd.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/d5ecb717d9e5734a3691bfcfc68301dd.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/d5ecb717d9e5734a3691bfcfc68301dd.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Defeat the boss and pass the levels together in the underground city.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/901a2a40f4c20d867591320f3ddfd830.poster.avif?t=1721397921\" width=400 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/901a2a40f4c20d867591320f3ddfd830.webm?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/901a2a40f4c20d867591320f3ddfd830.mp4?t=1721397921\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/a1aaff24b98abd0484392a488c8663fa.avif?t=1721397921\" width=558 height=298 /></span><br><br>The game contains a variety of items, such as spring, gravity control, weapon, iron head, iron shoes, shell, handgun, consecutive jumping, teleportation portal, and so on.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/a99d9aa07647947696372baf423dfdb5.avif?t=1721397921\" width=558 height=298 /></span><br><br>Feature-rich creative panel ignites your imagination.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/00fdf7196bdbe09aa1bcb35c2545118c.avif?t=1721397921\" width=558 height=514 /></span><br><br>Players can directly create pixel art in the game and use it directly in the editor.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991320/extras/c5bfd41debc3c0afdbed3e853d40475e.avif?t=1721397921\" width=800 height=186 /></span><br><br>Complete social functions allow players to compete with each other in terms of map-making and runner skills.",
